{"tid":2436494,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人造肉 Beyond Meat 簽大約    為麥當勞、KFC、Pizza Hut 供應植物蛋白肉","createTime":"2021-03-07T07:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:57:11.000Z","uid":66271,"like":89,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"68fa89bcc72fa4a4401970a5479c789c6dd96a84","tid":2436494,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/im-258061.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2Fim-258061.jpg&h=15491eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年社會提倡食人造肉，即是素食肉，從而減少對地球的負荷。美國人造肉公司 Beyond Meat 最近與麥當勞和百勝餐飲集團 (Yum!Brands) 簽下全球戰略協議，望將人造肉打入美國主流餐飲市場。<br />\n<br />\n根據與麥當勞的 3 年協議， Beyond Meat 會是「優先供應商」，為全球最大餐飲連鎖店食麥當勞的素漢堡提供素餡肉，為數以百萬計的食客提供人造肉，亦會鑽研其他素食餐點，包括雞肉、豬肉和蛋的植物性替代品。另外，Beyond Meat 在未來幾年會與百勝集團旗下的 KFC，Pizza Hut 等，共同研製獨家植物蛋白產品等。<br />\n<br />\n漢堡及香腸的廠商 Beyond Meat 是洛杉磯一家製造 100% 全植物成分的肉類替代品的製造商。自 2013 年開始，該公司產品已可在美國全國的全食超市購買。"},{"pid":"6c5c94e9fca6609bff0ca133e63044f90698afa3","tid":2436494,"uid":387826,"like":3,"dislike":46,"score":-43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"好味是良知.jpg"},{"pid":"112a39a09826bb07f82f112005899efc03f75fe9","tid":2436494,"uid":360041,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾隔幾個禮拜炒一次消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3c473a948f24185470421ce435e9949a942409","tid":2436494,"uid":52299,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"112a39a09826bb07f82f112005899efc03f75fe9","tid":2436494,"uid":360041,"like":169,"dislike":0,"score":169,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"呢間垃圾隔幾個禮拜炒一次消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"係 呢間垃圾出完財報後一定出幾條合作消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為差唔多次次財報都差過預期"},{"pid":"6c6